{"tid":264373,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先行李過磅過極都超重 屌佢老母","createTime":"2017-05-30T18:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T20:35:05.000Z","uid":4545,"like":4,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f50078c9982ed49faf4a313c99b1110ff7204f82","tid":264373,"uid":4545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T18:09:39.000Z","msg":"明明book機票就話寄倉25kg，我事前磅過係21kg左右<br />\n<br />\n點知到check in果時<br />\n<br />\n我一放個喼，counter條友就：重重！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我以為我記錯重量，可能係20kg，就執返幾件衫同褸走<br />\n<br />\n再磅過-&gt;19kg 心諗今次實無死<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老味  條友：重！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我即刻問佢超重幾多，點知條友串過馬撚，剩係話重重重重重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我即刻屌出聲，叫佢呀頭出黎<br />\n<br />\n佢呀頭出到黎話唔好意思，個職員係韓國人，跟住就好快手幫我搞掂晒d行李<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老味on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d1545776d9bb72a7890a315ead258e689e8f7b","tid":264373,"uid":75694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T18:11:00.000Z","msg":"仲以為係放咗對波上磅"},{"pid":"389cc6a09920fd3ccb088ca29c180bc905c18f40","tid":264373,"uid":1991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T18:11:03.000Z","msg":"職員：蠢蠢蠢蠢蠢"},{"pid":"c05d004532c135b32a1df9e314f272b6cc42a089","tid":264373,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T18:19:29.000Z","msg":"Tsum Tsum"},{"pid":"27054baba55f2b4dd37b6a255816a3b1494e463e","tid":264373,"uid":47794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T18:24:36.000Z","msg":"佢係咪想講  寵寵寵咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0197c0535ad4c678f0c49e148827a90d8b9e5716","tid":264373,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T18:25:27.000Z","msg":"蝦蝦蝦"},{"pid":"4c3190cb5d3dda9c4c1fd2a93fb59a61fb8d3e4b","tid":264373,"uid":36860,"like":0,"dislik